        "q": "How do I add a new device?",
        "a": "Go to the Devices section and click 'Add Device'. Enter the DevEUI and device details to register it."
      },
      {
        "q": "How does billing work?",
        "a": "Billing is per active device per month based on your plan. An invoice is generated at the start of each month."
      },
      {
        "q": "How do I set up alerts?",
        "a": "In the Alerts section, create a new rule by selecting a device, channel, operator, and threshold value."
      },
      {
        "q": "How do I change the language?",
        "a": "In Profile Settings, select your preferred language from the language dropdown."
      },
      {
        "q": "Where can I see raw device data?",
        "a": "Click 'View Logs' from the device list to see all incoming messages with hex data, RSSI, SNR, and decoded payload."
      }
